{"tid":1636192,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[理性分析]有冇人有聽今日果集城寨","createTime":"2019-10-07T17:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T04:59:22.000Z","uid":66833,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5fde965f0a1dc20fc7ff482bfccb4e614041c5f2","tid":1636192,"uid":66833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:00:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Gn_abeRrKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-Gn_abeRrKo&d=wXQbzQ6sjjdDHWUhljjVfyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=29219d97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Gn_abeRrKo</a><br />\n<br />\n我歷史知識唔夠，但我純聽頭三十分鐘已經覺得好合邏輯。<br />\n我無時間聽哂全部，以下為一個Short Summary，歡迎大家補充及討論。<br />\n１。漸進式緊急法，由林奠控制速度，以減低對社會衝擊。<br />\n２。八九後港人願意比時間中共發展，達至有普選既一日，但由五年前起，有一班香港人已經醒覺，知道中共與普世價值係大纜都扯唔埋。<br />\n３。中共與港共對處理政治鬥爭，歷史反映佢地都只會一直向左走，直至達至最極端情況，最後係佢地控制及打壓下Reset。<br />\n４。以北愛為例子，認為香港下一站將會去到北愛30年悲劇，直至2047由中共全面控制。"},{"pid":"83c1d4782912218adcedc31a8d0f1d886cc1d6b2","tid":1636192,"uid":66833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:03:29.000Z","msg":"推，希望有對歷史有研究既手足可以補足一下。"},{"pid":"3c593106464f4d3024a2e8cb9f155538d67bb89f","tid":1636192,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:06:16.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"e179b1483b0da2ae42acaa0ba6f9226c81b8e3ef","tid":1636192,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:07:28.000Z","msg":"Le 一集 <br />\n我agree 佢的分析中史的行事手法好make sense <br />\n值得一睇"},{"pid":"6aecb4494aaa8f1a5de53f3e1d92d63d206bc2fd","tid":1636192,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"再推一推"},{"pid":"e36bcbad87017798330c11b20bf8a63378eb0504","tid":1636192,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:07:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a3ae858d430f26be26c6e1d05194adaa45fe476","tid":1636192,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit